import React from 'react'
import { Grid, Image, Label, Card, Icon, Menu, Segment, Container, Button } from 'semantic-ui-react'
import "typeface-roboto";


const testClick = () =>{
  alert("TEST CLICK");
}


const Landing = () => (
  
<Container>
  <Grid stackable columns='4'   >
    <Grid.Column >

    <Card  onClick={()=>testClick()} fluid style = {{  backgroundColor: "#6d6d6d", boxShadow:".5px"}}>  
    <Image src='http://localhost:5000/images/1556324419626Bird.jpg' />

    <Card.Content  fluid  >
      
      <Card.Header style = {{color:'white'}}> I got my Bachelors Degree! </Card.Header>
      <Card.Meta>
        
        <Label color='olive'>dev</Label>
      </Card.Meta>
      
      <Card.Description style = {{color:'white'}}>Matthew is a musician living in Nashville. </Card.Description>
    </Card.Content>
 
    <Menu  fluid widths={3} text>
        <Menu.Item style = {{color:'gray'}}  name='24'  icon='heart'/>
        <Menu.Item style = {{color:'gray'}} name='12'  icon='comment'/>
        <Menu.Item style = {{color:'gray'}}name='120'  icon='eye'/>

      </Menu>

    
  </Card>
 

  </Grid.Column>
 

  </Grid>
</Container>
)

export default Landing
